Package: emyweather
Type: Package
Title: Climatic Data from the Greek National Meteorological Service
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Konstantinos", "Vantas", role = c("aut", "cre"),
  email = "kon.vantas@gmail.com",
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6387-8791"))
Maintainer: Konstantinos Vantas <kon.vantas@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains climatic data from the Greek National 
    Meteorological Service, as well as a number of useful other related data 
    sets. The climatic data come from 21 weather stations, with a time step of 
    3 hours. The time period is from 1975 to 2004.
URL: https://github.com/kvantas/emyweather
BugReports: https://github.com/kvantas/emyweather/issues             
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1),
  ggmap (>= 2.6.1)
